Scoring rationale (mapped to your rubric)

Technology Adoption — 18/25
- Rationale: L3Harris has multiple meaningful sustainable tech implementations (large VPPA, on‑site solar carport projects, energy efficiency retrofits, water reuse saving ~20M gallons/year, facility process water reductions of ~70%). These are significant operational implementations, but they are focused on established technologies (PPAs, solar, water reuse, efficiency) rather than multiple breakthrough proprietary technologies deployed at scale across product lines. Citations: [lightsourcebp](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG9jVt-0UjBDO3tlVPj7Xnu73_r_4ouBGo5NOowdPnCQ40H658dG69oIci0e4FmPB8oFMyl1Kny2j34pHc0cnC8Kl84egu06pZ0n0MBows9S_HLyPZgslam1wRxCNR84FKuzM52yCu53pIxfY7R4p08VqtWQd4imglYfzlfx20A) [l3harris](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH_36jhGaMHdE_B8-4-qwt0QJxca51Y9Odl0QXZoFLTqM7cza5iZzUwESRchzujXvmlEal5IFz-6zXnKz4ZbuH6Bmg9puDEG1zOhd5WlOiC3SbYhkpMTWqZwcY4SdYCKigwzLohkF-W0ffFYM4leql_6sWK0E-yiE4Cayjj1gcZ3gUbOgKasKosfSSPS0wI4jCbGzE1hDyUPxgHNDoHB2NbPzqCGPBeqJD0uX7SdpRD3BPsaQ==) [l3harris](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFS--4QhvyuyeU2DFmZzsgpzHRdva_l17ddOpXQqOzhkTEXPnRRgtnKehMzKb3ZxD-QLGxUIFljo7mWCmWwPxPHIhSW5SncYG9SYRkC5WjY8buJy0FOckr2GhKn6-kRZLJCfwivV2WwqZFxywZ_gKw4itX1FvTaJFD7ioCNmxTio-ucdUm-jRwmz5JqqwSEEx_AoWP8xSXfBs06M-LGeFSprVBN6ucN-gs=) [youtube](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG4h2Jst_xB-ldtatlCjJI1fc-nY6Lbrie-oyyPojblDSuSjJw0S7N-xxHOJisNTqXFbaTsGHcGdk4JPzwlto9--R7ff7heFs53gw9F_iblP8FMo8V4PE3N_UydNxQUT1AFfVc2eg==) [businesswire](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-eXKeQwoTg3qTncBjKDfO94bAvP3A1G2SSaxIz7uQrXMNMHUBXzWEoDjPdUOAk_9qyHt84mebJZQCvNAfZGUmtE7mYnTOm4WYtQLRCJ1zHQmYPCuqUHy40tX9-5a900QjiVrEx8Fc5p1OmKuj1oyGVpm-gMXlLP5rhHNZCtb6qpB7h36pVpIc-OKrjeKg1FIsiJsGxpSVAsxPop3J6ZD6BHnoG4x1WCTf8g==).

Innovation Leadership — 16/25
- Rationale: L3Harris demonstrates strong programs, partnerships (Palantir, Shield Capital, NOAA), and practical market innovation (VPPA), showing an above‑average commitment to piloting and integrating new approaches. However, public evidence of company‑owned breakthrough sustainable‑tech IP or major green‑tech R&D budgets is limited — the firm’s patent portfolio is large but weighted toward defense/avionics rather than discrete sustainable materials or carbon‑removal technologies. Citations: [l3harris](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGf5atoVJsLdYaqI63UGp--c-YH45xg_TQMOuBzuCWvpZt1itWrWdMBGhBs-qWp_zn7R6e6Cr-k3GVD28gJIL9QebqjfamhwV9bGsmRVcw0XOX08KHwQdt4n35ofOz_rcQiMsETH_3tZODJq_VnIwoYIiSpBBWa0v7KMSHBhrBAY6vurlR8gOUbE7LnFqN9uqxZB0_OQrLf0A==) [responsibilityreports](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETL8zW5s8Ix-azp7Tx4Z8eRZJ2MCC06hG2i70iaJeiFsyGTBNjfhyRfr-oh6Ce6zkWVLtX6bWTtPHgIOSXHrq5Mhemkij5g6TDvgF4H1iB_uSJg_lY1wRhzGD6Z6mH0xXtDNb-05pOxqa6BWsutd3seP0lNeNKtEuTiJmdv13kL1RQUkYfo4dBIABq6k92AIa0XFgUKryMLaUytg==) [patentguru](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQExL7T_aC-ggUHoV3DaghBpx1Mv98BF9RlMPjj6j2iRmB7ur85eFNDvvPqo033LH4xscNhxfAhSt2Mgv8TX9hziLPiDOuXVIUAfRrTz2Ma9VJTriwpATRTLQKDv4tqs1f3cZCJ7IoMcwHWqIKrwqMqGN3oLiTL1kwVkQPpO) [justia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFtQJzpVJKnbCOxQXMydZzIAY-dsMA7vJsmuDaBVMX3TZrBzWwLpbxvUObd7pMul_ajdJMCc83mvYFxdZaiTGmLrqn2igGJDKEB4lLJJk4A4MqjyPKA1E91zAboiKXbVJvXJT4xt7vOMfKz).

Measurable Impact — 18/25
- Rationale: Measured results include exceeding the previous 30% GHG reduction goal early, enterprise GHG reporting (2023/2024 totals), Elm Branch VPPA (~110k tCO2e/year avoided), and concrete water savings (20M gallons/year Operation Splashdown, 43 megaliters reduction reported). These are meaningful, quantifiable impacts — likely in the “strong measurable impact” band (25–50% improvements on some metrics historically) — but companywide absolute emissions remain material and full scope‑3 reductions and sustained long‑term performance will determine final outcomes. Citations: [businesswire](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHTYtSVZyMZmYVCWFkEEkJbb0dumhM_FQuGiTo1I0uVykcFTuBMw1f_0Oe4Jc7ANOfEhMC23vyveNPMsORz8Wn4qFlU2ckzY5L96O-FH-zSwXnGARLu6s56k2Yu5loUgR73KEl6XbIYFkNYnrLzLwo7jJ8IoZKZhWgOD-ct75fVQHynb3UY-P3vfHcKXKZVqQcJwpbjolcT78VFlx0roLty) [lightsourcebp](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG9jVt-0UjBDO3tlVPj7Xnu73_r_4ouBGo5NOowdPnCQ40H658dG69oIci0e4FmPB8oFMyl1Kny2j34pHc0cnC8Kl84egu06pZ0n0MBows9S_HLyPZgslam1wRxCNR84FKuzM52yCu53pIxfY7R4p08VqtWQd4imglYfzlfx20A) [ditchcarbon](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGsp4oZy_yizG6mJPEn3B2u5a-hhW4bpLnaJ9b8UhHR3cNn5pf1cpgq7OjUBpf0wJR8ExqDBVfBVqWWF_wiAvx0g3KXqmLjWm5WPQS6UUH_CmCpIArw1ZBNAgT_WVpj41gCtzySxPLum6A=) [l3harris](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFS--4QhvyuyeU2DFmZzsgpzHRdva_l17ddOpXQqOzhkTEXPnRRgtnKehMzKb3ZxD-QLGxUIFljo7mWCmWwPxPHIhSW5SncYG9SYRkC5WjY8buJy0FOckr2GhKn6-kRZLJCfwivV2WwqZFxywZ_gKw4itX1FvTaJFD7ioCNmxTio-ucdUm-jRwmz5JqqwSEEx_AoWP8xSXfBs06M-LGeFSprVBN6ucN-gs=).

